replies.bodyText:
We are fixing how ' ' gets encoded by replacing the incorrect '+' with the correct '%20'
For example:
String urlEncoded = URLEncoder.encode("This string has spaces", StandardCharsets.UTF_8.displayName());
String actuallyUrlEncoded = urlEncoded.replaceAll("\\+", "%20");

urlEncoded = "This+string+has+spaces"
actuallyUrlEncoded = "This%20string%20has%20spaces"
